{"id":14836,"date":"2026-02-20T14:51:20","date_gmt":"2026-02-20T19:51:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=evenement&#038;p=14836"},"modified":"2026-02-20T14:51:20","modified_gmt":"2026-02-20T19:51:20","slug":"coup-de-poing-main-une-activite-interactive-avec-le-y-des-femmes","status":"publish","type":"evenement","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/evenement\/coup-de-poing-main-une-activite-interactive-avec-le-y-des-femmes\/","title":{"rendered":"Coup de poing main : une activit\u00e9 interactive avec le Y des femmes"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Afin de sensibiliser aux r\u00e9actions aidantes et nuisibles face aux cyberviolences, le Y des femmes de Montr\u00e9al a d\u00e9velopp\u00e9 <em>Coup de <s>poing<\/s> main, <\/em>une exp\u00e9rience immersive en 360\u00b0.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Une exp\u00e9rience immersive et interactive en trois temps<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>L\u2019exp\u00e9rience immersive de r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle, <em>Coup de <s>poing<\/s> main<\/em> immerge dans la peau d\u2019une c\u00e9g\u00e9pienne qui se confie \u00e0 ses amis et amies apr\u00e8s avoir partag\u00e9 des photos intimes \u00e0 son petit-ami. L\u2019objectif pour les participantes et participants est de choisir les diff\u00e9rentes r\u00e9actions de l\u2019entourage qui s\u2019av\u00e8rent \u00eatre aidantes ou nuisibles.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":14839,"template":"","categorieevenement":[193],"etiquette-interne":[2287,2357],"class_list":["post-14836","evenement","type-evenement","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorieevenement-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-milieu-de-vie"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:22:55","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"categorieevenement"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenemen